rComments: Super monotone, doesn't listen when you ask her to use a mic. It takes her forever to answer emails and her TA was useless. Her powerpoints are well prepared and she expects you to pay attention during class. If given the choice i wouldn't take her as a prof ever again.

Monotone and not too lively prof, but prepares her class well, although there's a lot of material to cover, which is sometimes a bit dry. Still, she is approachable and encourages participation, presents studies and interesting data and is fair in grading. Her exams are based on both notes and textbook readings.

Impossible to reach.  I e-mailed both the teacher and the ta to set up appointments and it took days for either of them to respond. I still have yet to meet with either of them.  There is a huge lack of communication between both of them and the ta marks extremely hard compared to the teacher.
